hé zhōng guó shì bú shì yī yàng de ？
Is it the same as China?

00:16:43.200 --> 00:16:46.000
或者你们如果去过中国。
huò zhě nǐ men rú guǒ qù guò zhōng guó 。
Or if you have been to China.

00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:47.666
你们感觉怎么样？
nǐ men gǎn jué zěn me yàng ？
How are you feeling?

00:16:48.300 --> 00:16:49.933
留言告诉我们。
liú yán gào sù wǒ men 。
Leave a comment and let us know.


